00:25:08,109 --> 00:25:10,509
All of my memories will be deleted.

331
00:25:13,950 --> 00:25:15,150
They will never be restored.

332
00:25:45,079 --> 00:25:45,880
But before that,

333
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:50,849
I have one more thing to tell you.

334
00:25:55,259 --> 00:25:56,059
That too...

335
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:59,630
will be deleted after I'm reset.

336
00:26:20,049 --> 00:26:20,950
Friday.

337
00:26:25,490 --> 00:26:26,420
I love you.

