Lu Sen's file has been deleted.

345
00:27:55,309 --> 00:27:56,009
You're back.

346
00:28:02,049 --> 00:28:03,420
What's wrong?

347
00:28:03,849 --> 00:28:04,549
Shan Shan.

348
00:28:56,069 --> 00:28:57,069
Hi, Fri...

349
